    description: "Bring the big screen home. Our container cinema rooms can be crafted for pure escapism - dark, quiet and acoustically treated. Perfect for film buffs, directors, or anyone who takes movie nights seriously. Designed for atmosphere, built for comfort - find more details on your bespoke private cinema room."
  },
  {
    src: "classroom.webp",
    title: "Classrooms",
    description: "Teach in peace. Our container classrooms can be designed for calm, focused learning - quiet, warm and free from outside distractions: ideal for one-to-one tuition, small groups or online learning. A smarter, faster alternative to traditional builds - delve into bespoke classroom spaces that work."
  },
  {
    src: "craft-studio.webp",
    title: "Craft Studios",
    description: "Create without compromise. Our container craft studios can be tailored to your flow - bright, warm and distraction-free. Whether you're painting, stitching, sculpting or designing, this is your dedicated space to focus and flourish. Inspiring, secure and built around you. Navigate to your made-to-measure studio now."
  },
  {
    src: "gaming-room.webp",
    title: "Gaming Rooms",
    description: "Level up your setup. Our container gaming rooms can be styled for total immersion - dark walls, ambient lighting and zero distractions. Built for streamers, creators and serious players who want their own private world. Bold, atmospheric, and made to order. Discover your custom-built game zone now."
  },
  {
    src: "garden-room.webp",
    title: "Garden Rooms",
    description: "Not your average garden room. Our container conversions blend modern design with practical performance - think clean lines, sleek finishes and fully insulated comfort. Ideal for creative spaces, studios or home offices. Made to impress, made to last - investigate our designer garden rooms now."
  },
  {
    src: "gym.webp",
    title: "Gyms",
    description: "Train hard. Build smart. Our bespoke steel gym buildings and container gym conversions are built to take a beating - just like you. Fully insulated, ventilated and ready for kit. Ideal for PTs, sports clubs or home setups. Durable, relocatable and made to spec - why not examine your gym built the industrial way?"
  },
  {
    src: "insulated-storage.webp",
    title: "Insulated Storage",
    description: "Need more than just a basic box? Our lined and insulated storage containers offer dry, secure and temperature-stable space all year round. Perfect for tools, stock, equipment or sensitive items. Clean, ready-to-use and customisable. Discover a smarter way to store - tick box, explore our range now."
  },
  {
    src: "bar.webp",
    title: "Luxury Bars & Lounges",
    description: "Designed to impress. Built to perform. Our luxury container bars and lounges can be styled with fitted bars, ambient lighting, luxe finishes and serious atmosphere. Ideal for bold private builds or standout brand launches - tune in & cheque out our high-spec spaces that turn heads."
  },
  {
    src: "office.webp",
    title: "Luxury Offices",
    description: "Portable prestige. Built to impress. Our luxury container offices can be tailored with premium finishes, smart layouts and executive detail. Designed for entrepreneurs, directors and decision-makers who want more than just a workspace. Built to command respect from day one. Make it yours now."
  },
  {
    src: "home.webp",
    title: "Man Caves",
    description: "Your space. Your rules. Our bespoke man cave container conversions can be tailored for downtime, hobbies or serious-big screen time. Dark, bold, built around you: whether it's music, motors, gambling or just relaxing. Hard drinks, harder playlists. Peruse the ultimate retreat on your terms now."
  },
  {
    src: "meeting-room.webp",
    title: "Meeting Rooms",
