  },
  {
    src: "retail-popup-shop.webp",
    title: "Retail Pop-Up Shops",
    description: "Pop-Up shops that scream style. Bold, branded and impossible to ignore - these container conversions aren't just shops, they're show-stoppers. From artisan espresso bars to streetwear temples, we build mobile spaces that demand attention. Perfect for festivals, high streets, markets and brand pioneers. you bring the vision — we'll build the buzz."
  },
  {
    src: "she-shed.webp",
    title: "She Sheds",
    description: "A Containerised She Shed! Girl power in a box: and no, he's not invited. Fully-insulated, electrified and 100% yours. She Shed container conversions built for peace, pampering or plotting your empire. Art studio? Yoga pod? Wine & whinge den? You choose. Built your way, delivered UK-wide. No men - no boys!"
  },
  {
    src: "site-office.webp",
    title: "Site Offices",
    description: "Steel-built, site-ready, lined & insulated offices: anti-vandal, secure, portable and made for serious work. We convert shipping containers and fabricate steel site offices, to order. You choose electrics, heating, lighting, layout and internal finishes. Ideal for construction, logistics, manufacturing, and remote teams. Built to your spec - delivered nationwide."
  },
  {
    src: "workshop.webp",
    title: "Workshops",
    description: "Workshops that mean business. Steel-built, badged-up and ready to graft. From greasy spanners to sparks and sawdust, these converted container workshops are made to take the hits and keep working. Fit them with benches, racks, power, light and grit. Built for mechanics, makers, engineers and repair crews - bespoke customised relocatable: all yours."
